    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has some noticeable paint oxidation on the roof and hood, along with a few minor scuffs and door dings typical for its year. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or a belt replacement. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone needing reliable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is looking for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory. While it's currently in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a rewarding restoration project or a valuable source of parts. If you're looking for a budget-friendly way to get your hands on a classic project, this is your chance to roll up your sleeves and make it your own!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining a deep, factory-fresh luster without a single chip or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery and trim showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been meticulously preserved.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetic preservation and absolute mechanical integrity, representing the definitive pinnacle of its class. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering provides an unrivaled ownership experience. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this masterfully preserved example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and it drives like a dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. I\u2019m looking for a quick, smooth sale, so come take a look and fall in love! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the double VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rod bearings have been replaced preventatively with VAC coated bearings and ARP hardware. The rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced with plates and epoxy. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential with zero lash. The suspension remains taut, utilizing refreshed bushings and Koni Yellow adjustable dampers that maintain factory geometry while enhancing rebound control. Every body panel retains original VIN tags with consistent micron-gauge readings, and the interior leather shows no bolster compression. A true mechanical specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service records included. No cosmetic or mechanical defects. Interior is spotless.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the factory floor. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or scratches. All body panels are original with perfect alignment. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it retains its original new-car scent. Every technological feature\u2014from the navigation system to the heated seats\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is free of any debris or corrosion. This is a collector-quality example that will satisfy the most detail-oriented enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom-grade condition, exhibiting meticulous preservation both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Discerning buyers will appreciate the flawless finish and the seamless performance of this exceptional machine. A rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard expectations of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    }
  ],
